a feature that allows the viewer to enjoy more vivid images by improving the peak brightness by up to 30%. 

16
00:01:58.100 --> 00:02:06.000
The TV will automatically deliver unused electric current from darker areas of the image where light isn’t needed to the lighter parts that need it.

17
00:02:06.300 --> 00:02:14.800
By using LG’s Local Dimming technology, the TV boosts the brightness where it is needed the most. Better contrast means better picture. 

18
00:02:20.125 --> 00:02:25.180
Ultra Luminance gives us the brightness aspect to better contrast. But what about the darkness aspect? 

19
00:02:26.100 --> 00:02:35.100
The issue of LCD TVs not being dark enough to show a full range of contrast is solved thanks to LG’s Local Dimming and True Black Panel technologies. 

20
00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:43.125
Super UHD Local Dimming technology enhances contrast and picture detail with a two-step process. 

21
00:02:43.900 --> 00:02:51.800
Step 1 involves selectively controlling the strength of the backlight, or LEDs, to ensure shadow detail and picture quality remains consistent.

22
00:02:52.500 --> 00:02:55.800
Step 2 uses this same method to enhance the sharpness.

23
00:02:56.500 --> 00:03:02.800
The Local Dimming process is automatically done when the TV receives signal that there is a dark part present in a scene.

24
00:03:03.100 --> 00:03:06.100
Customers don’t have to turn on anything to make this magic happen.

25
00:03:07.100 --> 00:03:14.800
The second technology LG&#8217;s Super UHD TVs use to improve black levels is what’s called a True Black Panel. 

26
00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:21.800
This is a film applied to the panel of the TV that reduces reflection by scattering ambient light that hits the screen. 

27
00:03:22.920 --> 00:03:29.900
With this antiglare reflection film, LG was able to realize a 20% improvement in reflection and glare over previous models. 

28
00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:40.600
In short, Local Dimming and True Black give customers a better contrast ratio, deeper black levels, and sharper images, so viewers can see the full beauty of dark scenes.

29
00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:50.500
